data.title: Lat Long Info
data.meta_description: Lat Long Info - Free ebook download as Excel Spreadsheet (.xls), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. This document lists the names of over 200 cities and towns across multiple countries including Andorra, Afghanistan, United Arab Emirates, Iran, Azerbaijan, Armenia, Angola, Portugal, Albania, and Argentina. The cities and towns are listed alphabetically with their latitude and longitude coordinates provided.
